"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Hello Loopers.  You may or may not recognize me, as it has been quite a while since I have found the time post here.  Back in the day this used to be my go to place for writing everything and anything when it comes to crypto.  Some may know me round these parts, but many may not.  Fair enough if you fall into the latter, it really has been a while. \\n\\nIt is not that I do not write anymore, it is more that when I do find the time to do so, it is for one of the handful of projects that I am presently working with in the space.  It's funny in a way, as not only did this place use to be my go to, but it is also where I got my start.  There is a long list of articles deep within my profile that tells a very interesting story for those that want to take a gander.  \\n\\nThat said, I still do write, and quite a bit.  Mostly I have been writing articles denoting awesome builds in a little project I am working with called [The Uplift World.](https://theuplift.world/)  For those who might not know, The Uplift World is a blockchain based metaverse utilizing Minecraft for a Play2Earn experience like no other.  \",\"timestamp\":1638432598,\"title\":\"The Amazing Builders of The Uplift World Blockchain Metaverse (and other small tales)\\nCrypto Gaming\"},\"digest\":\"XKyFwV3ra-TLXR9IEiA-Zo2KSOOTAyVzbv38_k5LvTE\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xfBF685fE24E48b0857998fA6B8d3e83e7a755f11\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"7Tbx_cdBZHd4UCeZl3yanrHBxoUHJBix_-llP4psmIU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"cZ786yluP1hTlTjENX60U8eqGHIwG2T8OnM_g_Bb8KE\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"vrg-udzOh58we7jsv_GEyuH-NZ27cuL19HT8-KI5lIxOkRKE6iSa3ToxevmkcpIJs6ihJHR-rXCjEDi_k0bK1w\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x1507edab583d7b24116cd0d39ac8810228d0b3746aa34bf2413e377f1c2c3b8a4cb390102e4b4fde802e90828111170d820da5d4c60bb88212216d85f62251131c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz f